    "original_source_path": "newapp/dataset=decision/decision/commonwealth/1905/decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908.json",
    "text": "English Scottish and A lian Bank (1). In that ease evidence was given to show that plaintiff left his home with intent to delay his creditors, and th facts were consistent with his having done so. The manager 0) defendant bank swore that he honestly believed that the plaint had done so, the jury found that he did not, and found a verdict the plaintift.",
