  {
    "id": "dataset=decision_decision_commonwealth_1905_decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908_83",
    "doc_id": "dataset=decision_decision_commonwealth_1905_decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908",
    "original_source_path": "newapp/dataset=decision/decision/commonwealth/1905/decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908.json",
    "text": "For these reasons I think that the plaintiff in the present failed to discharge the onus cast upon him, and that reasons stated he ought to have been nonsuited. Barton J. I concur.",
