  {
    "id": "dataset=decision_decision_commonwealth_1905_decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908_91",
    "doc_id": "dataset=decision_decision_commonwealth_1905_decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908",
    "original_source_path": "newapp/dataset=decision/decision/commonwealth/1905/decision_commonwealth_1905_9ff1e908.json",
    "text": "They might fi that it was for the public benefit in some supposed case wh might never arise. Such a finding might have no relation tot publication the subject of the action. All the circums' : the publication must be taken into consideration by the j dealing with the question whether the publication was foi public benefit.",
    "version_id": "high_court_of_australia:/showbyHandle/1/14123",
